
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Address from Mnemonic</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/styles.css" />
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <h1>Derive Address from Mnemonic</h1>
        <p>Generate a new mnemonic or enter an existing one to calculate its private key, public key, and corresponding address.</p>

        <hr>

        <h2>Generate a New Mnemonic</h2>
        <button id="generateMnemonicButton" class="btn-submit">Generate New Mnemonic</button>

        <hr>

        <h2>Use an Existing Mnemonic</h2>
        <div class="input-group">
            <label for="mnemonic-input">Mnemonic:</label>
            <input type="text" id="mnemonic-input" placeholder="Enter your 12 or 24-word mnemonic phrase">
        </div>
        <button id="useMnemonicButton" class="btn-submit">Use This Mnemonic</button>

        <div id="mnemonicResult" class="result-container" style="display: none;">
            <h2>Mnemonic Used</h2>
            <p><strong>Mnemonic:</strong> <span id="mnemonic"></span></p>
        </div>
        
        <div id="result" class="result-container" style="display: none;">
            <h2>Derived Information</h2>
            <p><strong>Private Key (Hex):</strong> <span id="privateKeyHex"></span></p>
            <p><strong>Private Key (WIF):</strong> <span id="privateKeyWIF"></span></p>
            <p><strong>Public Key:</strong> <span id="publicKey"></span></p>
            <p><strong>Address (testnet4):</strong> <span id="address"></span></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="/js/mnemonic_ui.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
